snippet.title: WarriOrb - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy on Steam: https://bit.ly/WarriOrbSteamTrailer
Buy on Xbox: https://bit.ly/WarriOrbXboxTrailer
Buy on Switch: http://bit.ly/WarriOrbSwitchTrailer
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/NotYet
Released: 28 April 2020

Play as a mighty demon trapped in an unlikely body – a talking ball with agile limbs – in this Soulsborne-inspired jaunt where death is the least of your worries...

Available in English, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, French, Russian, Spanish, Hungarian and Romanian.
